name: Pinchy Crab
description: Juniper's Genesis NFT.  This was meant to be free, but a bot snagged most of them.  It is free again with the new tool at https://dono.xtz.tools/. Pinchy Crab is a game Juniper often plays before bathtime... "Watch out Mamma, watch out daddy, here comes pinchy crab!" Occasionally the pinchy crab takes a break for a dance party. This is Juniper's depiction of Pinchy Crab utilizing chalk on concrete.
